{
  "The time value of money means:": "",
  "A dollar today is worth more than a dollar in the future because it can earn a return": "",
  "All money has equal value regardless of when it is received": "",
  "Future money is always worth more than present money": "",
  "Money loses all value over time": "",
  "The core TVM principle states that a dollar today is worth more than a dollar in the future because today's dollar can be invested to earn interest or returns over time.": "",
