  "Adding extra fees to a loan balance": "",
  "Earning interest only on the original principal": "",
  "Earning interest on both the principal and previously accumulated interest": "",
  "Combining multiple investments into one account": "",
  "Compounding is the process of earning interest on interest. Each period, the interest earned is added to the principal, and the next period's interest is calculated on the larger amount.": "",
